cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it deals with evolutionary optimization. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as these fields often use evolutionary algorithms for optimization. Additionally, since the paper deals with image optimization, it could belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, since the paper discusses the use of indicators for optimization, it could also belong to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
